 AN Islamic Organisation, Nasrul-Lahi-L-Fatih Society, NASFAT has commiserated with victims of the explosion which occurred on Sunday at Abule Ado, Amuwo Odofin Local Government Area of Lagos State. NASFAT condoled with all those who lost loved ones in the incident and sympathised with the injured and those who lost properties to the inferno. NASFAT also commiserated with the Lagos State Government over the tragic incident and praised all the emergency agencies for their prompt   response and intervention. We pray to Almighty Allah for His protection over the country. May He comfort all those who are affected. NASFAT also called on the government at all levels and all relevant agencies to do proper diligence to forestall a recurrence.  